OL,7,FThis money then gets refunded by the
OL,8,FNHS, through the Hampshire and Isle of
OL,9,FWight Integrated Care Board (ICB) - as
OL,10,Fis common practice.
OL,12,FThe amount of rent the GP surgery pays
OL,13,Fis based on a valuation by the
OL,14,Fgovernment's District Valuer (DV), who
OL,15,Fsays the rent since 2016, should be
OL,16,Flower.
OL,18,FThis assessment is based on guidance
OL,19,Ffrom the Royal Institution of
OL,20,FChartered Surveyors.
