OL,3,C'We can't keep going': GP practice
OL,4,Cfears closure due to eight-year rent
OL,5,Cdispute
OL,7,FAt the centre of the dispute is a
OL,8,Fdisabled toilet, which the DV doesn't
OL,9,Fbelieve should be included in the rent
OL,10,Fof the premises.
OL,12,FThe DV says the value should be less
OL,13,Fthan what it was back in 2011, which
OL,14,Fthe landlord doesn't agree this is
OL,15,Ffair.
