OL,3,C'We can't keep going': GP practice
OL,4,Cfears closure due to eight-year rent
OL,5,Cdispute
OL,7,FWithout an agreed long-term lease, a
OL,8,Fpartner of the practice, Dr Ali
OL,9,FRobins, is having to also pay for an
OL,10,Fempty space next door to the surgery,
OL,11,Fwhich cannot take on new tenants and
OL,12,Fcan't be let out to a pharmacy.
OL,14,FDr Robins said she is also worried the
OL,15,Fpartners will be asked to repay eight
OL,16,Fyears of reimbursements, if the ICB
OL,17,Fdecides it has given them too much
OL,18,Fmoney back.
