OL,3,C'We can't keep going': GP practice
OL,4,Cfears closure due to eight-year rent
OL,5,Cdispute
OL,7,FDr Robins said: "We've spent just
OL,8,Funder #100,000 on legal fees,
OL,9,Fsurveyors fees and the rent and the
OL,10,Fbills for next door.
OL,12,F"I have now run out of money. We can't
OL,13,Fkeep going for much longer."
OL,15,FThe landlord of St Peter's Surgery is
OL,16,Fgrowing tired too and suggests court
OL,17,Faction might be necessary, if the NHS'
OL,18,Fnational arbitrators can't help to
OL,19,Ffind an agreement.
