OL,7,FMuch like the partners, the landlord
OL,8,Falso wants the lease to be renewed,
OL,9,Fbut at a fair price.
OL,11,FSimon Harwood, director at ASA Group,
OL,12,Fis a healthcare surveyor and works
OL,13,Falongside the landlord.
OL,15,FHe said: "Even if the rent was going
OL,16,Fup by #1 a week and we're saying it
OL,17,Fshould go up by #2 a week, there is a
OL,18,Fdispute.
