OL,7,F"The key issue here is, if there is a
OL,8,Fdispute, parties can only spend so
OL,9,Flong trying to find a resolution
OL,10,Famongst themselves."
OL,12,FAll parties involved insist they want
OL,13,Fto end the uncertainty, to prevent
OL,14,Fthousands of patients being left
OL,15,Fwithout a GP.
OL,17,FThe ICB says it won't ask partners at
OL,18,Fthe GP practice to repay any over-
OL,19,Fimbursements.
