OL,3,C'We can't keep going': GP practice
OL,4,Cfears closure due to eight-year rent
OL,5,Cdispute
OL,7,FInstead, its director of primary care,
OL,8,FJames Roach says the NHS body is
OL,9,Fcommitted to resolution.
OL,11,FMr Roach said: "We have to ensure that
OL,12,Fwe provide high quality services in a
OL,13,Fway that represents value for the
OL,14,Ftaxpayer.
OL,16,F"The closure of St Peter's has never
OL,17,Fbeen discussed and is not on the
OL,18,Ftable. We're working hard with the
OL,19,Fpractice to ensure the services
OL,20,Fcontinue to be maintained."
