OL,7,FA Valuation Office Agency spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "District Valuer Services (DVS)
OL,9,Fadvises the NHS on the level of
OL,10,Fcurrent market rent (CMR) that should
OL,11,Fbe reimbursed for GP premises.
OL,13,F"Our work is carried out in line with
OL,14,FRoyal Institution of Chartered
OL,15,FSurveyors (RICS) guidance. We use all
OL,16,Frelevant evidence available at the
OL,17,Fvaluation date.
