OL,7,F"We are working very hard to deal with
OL,8,Fcases as quickly as possible. If we
OL,9,Fcannot reach agreement with a GP or
OL,10,Ftheir representative, they can appeal
OL,11,Fto NHS Resolution."
OL,13,FThe DVS told ITV Meridian it is not
OL,14,Fparty to the lease or any dispute
OL,15,Fbetween landlords and GP tenants.
OL,17,FSt Peter's is due to hold an open
OL,18,Fforum between patients, the landlord
OL,19,Fand local councillors on Monday 20th
OL,20,FMay 7pm-9pm at St Patrick's Catholic
OL,21,FPrimary School.
